Are you interested in learning valuable leadership skills applicable to everyday life? Attend Huskie Robotics’ leadership workshop series! Current and aspiring leaders are encouraged to attend!

Meetings will start October 17. The time is 8:00 PM - 9:30 PM CT and all meetings will be on zoom!

Anyone and everyone is welcome to attend - we would love to have you there! Our sessions will be lead by our coaches and mentors who have lots of valuable experience to share.
Please be sure to sign up using the link in the flyer. Can’t wait to see you there!
